# Test Cases

---

## Test Case 1: Property List Display (Logged-in User)

### Objective
Verify that a logged-in user can view property details correctly on the property list page.

### Preconditions
- Application loads successfully (200 OK)
- User has a valid registered account

### Test Data
- URL: http://localhost:4200
- Valid user credentials

### Steps
1. Open the application
2. Click on the "Login" button
3. Enter valid credentials and log in
4. Navigate to the property list page (e.g. "For Sale")

### Expected Result
- Property name is displayed
- Number of rooms is visible
- Price per room is shown
- Description and image are displayed correctly
- Page loads successfully without errors

